<D>__{yes you are, but still you can't run you won't run.}
<P>__{(studies her)}
<D>__{i wonder why that is?}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{i'm no devil. i'm no monster. amy, i will never hurt you and i will never leave you.}
